    "betterquesting:10": {
      "desc:8": "Welcome to the Pre-Nuclear Age! This questline bridges the gap between intermediate oil processing and full nuclear technology. Master advanced materials like Silicon and Fiberglass, set up factory automation with Conveyors and Drones, build key machines like the Gas Centrifuge and FEL/SILEX for isotope separation, and learn the complete Uranium and Plutonium enrichment chains. The final quests cover advanced nuclear fuels including MOX and Americium \u2014 preparing you for the nuclear age ahead!",
